https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=16397	6300
微软<a href="http://www.microsoft.com/presspass/press/2010/feb10/02-22MSAmazonPR.mspx">宣布</a>和亚马逊公司达成了达成范围广泛的<a href="http://news.slashdot.org/story/10/02/23/1231255/Microsoft-Amazon-Ink-Kindle-and-Linux-Patent-Deal">交叉专利许可协议</a>。<i>
